---
title: Roasted Dill-Garlic Double Salmon with Warm Orzo and Spinach Salad
description: This Greek-inspired pasta salad comes together in no time with the help of creamy yogurt sauce, and it serves as the perfect side for simple dill-garlic salmon. A touch of olives and feta confirms that tonight's dinner is fit for Grecian gods!
